00198     template<class Comparator> AsmFunctionIndex& sort(Comparator comp, bool unique=false) {
00199         std::stable_sort(functions.begin(), functions.end(), comp);
00200         if (unique) {
00201             Functions newlist;
00202             for (Functions::iterator fi=functions.begin(); fi!=functions.end(); fi++) {
00203                 if (newlist.empty() || comp.unique(newlist.back(), *fi))
00204                     newlist.push_back(*fi);
00205             }
00206             if (newlist.size()!=functions.size())
00207                 functions = newlist;
00208         }
00209         return *this;
00210     }
